      <title>Segantii 赎回请求在关闭前已达 10 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/segantii-redemption-requests-hit-1-billion-before-move-to-shut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，Segantii Capital Management Ltd. 的对冲基金在决定关闭之前面临近 10 亿美元的提款请求，这凸显了本月香港内幕交易指控对投资者信心的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/segantii-redemption-requests-hit-1-billion-before-move-to-shut</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 01:47:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
