      <title>Silk 称新西兰央行“绝对”准备在必要时加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/rbnz-absolutely-prepared-to-hike-rates-if-necessary-silk-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰央行助理行长凯伦·西尔克(Karen Silk)表示，如果经济发展意味着当前政策环境的限制性不足以使通胀回到目标水平，新西兰央行准备加息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/rbnz-absolutely-prepared-to-hike-rates-if-necessary-silk-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 01:39:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
